Rhea Ripley opens MONDAY NIGHT MAMI by challenging Liv Morgan for the WWE Women's World Championship

Dom comes out and acts like he's going to accept the challenge for Liv because she's too hurt. But Liv attacks Rhea from behind. They hang her by the leg in the ropes and Liv gives Rhea a kiss before running away

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0160be57-4c58-4b3c-be0a-9f3e865ed3d6/Screenshot_20240902_171802.jpg?format=original)

