![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2fcf8341-dced-4c7f-b985-bba18da33f14/Screenshot_20240902_171827.jpg?format=original)

Chad Gable hypes up American Made by slapping one of them and having the other one flip a table.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1a23aa15-2ffb-4b12-96ad-050f25d6eda5/20240902_173633.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AMERICAN MADE DEF. ALPHA_** ACADEMY
    

Ivy Nile puts Maxxine Dupri to sleep. After the match, Chad Gable challenges the Wyatt 6 to an 8 man Street Fight!!!

Uncle Howdy comes out and accepts the challenge.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a1b5d024-aee7-4454-80ed-b3b8d2744eed/20240902_173651.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6c0402fa-5c39-4771-b9e8-1f71b849f6df/20240902_175423.jpg?format=original)

Sonya Deville: There's not a man in this building who can take us home or a woman in the locker room who can take us at all. But if you want to shoot your shot? Step up.

*   ## **_SHAYNA BASLER DEF. ZELINA VEGA_**
    

Pretty quick match. Lyra Valkyria runs out to save Zelina from a post match beat down but she's unsuccessful.

Sonya Deville cuts a promo after.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/40e1690e-8cdf-42f5-a858-66cf264aee6f/20240902_175454.jpg?format=original)

