CM Punk officially challenges GUNTHER to a World Championship match. But he's immediately attacked by Drew McIntyre who breaks Punk’s bracelet and shoves the beads down his throat.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/32ece168-cb1d-49c0-b3b5-87dd9b6d9d58/Screenshot_20240902_181753.jpg?format=original)

