*   ## **_Intercontinental Championship Tournament: ILJA DRAGUNOV DEF. DRAGON LEE AND DOMINIK MYSTERIO_**
    

Ilja is in the Fatal Four Way Finals for the IV Title.

Once Ilja and Dragon Lee got rid of Dominik, these two men ABSOLUTELY COOKED.

We need them to run this back, one on one.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a29f6a3c-e466-4e67-83a6-4e8c4cf96d29/20240902_183858.jpg?format=original)

Braun Strowman is Bronson Reed’s replacement in the IC Title Tournament.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cd2243f9-c660-4335-b7b7-851230b7fb28/Screenshot_20240902_185959.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_NUMBER ONE CONTENDERSHIP FOR THE WOMEN'S TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: UNHOLY UNION DEF. DAMAGE CTRL_**
    

Jade Cargill and Bianca Belair are out to watch the match. Isla pushes Kairi into them off the top rope. This distracts Iyo causing the loss

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bcf063bd-d333-41ef-a7ed-5d6decc4e732/20240902_192832.jpg?format=original)

Gunther is basking in the glory of his victory over Randy Orton when Sami Zayn comes out to challenge for the World Championship. Gunther laughs at Sami's music.

Gunther says he respects Sami Zayn's passion. But no thanks.

Sami says he will be coming after the title one way or another

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ed0bdca1-1ccf-448b-9687-a8f3f0aa7e17/Screenshot_20240902_191709.jpg?format=original)

Bron Breakker tells Jey Uso that nobody in his family has ever beaten anyone in the Steiner family

Uso needs to leave Strowman alone and go chase after Dom's sloppy seconds.

Jey tells Bron thanks for the advice, ROOKIE.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/13d90be8-5c89-4727-ad71-fc1e7e1c5308/Screenshot_20240902_193754.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP TOURNAMENT: BRAUN STROWMAN DEF. SHEAMUS AND LUDWIG KAISER_**
    

Pete Dunne attacks Sheamus with a sheleighly, distracting Ludwig and allowing Braun Strowman to hit his poweslam for the win.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2b0386cc-be39-40c8-85b4-b0beab62aae4/Screenshot_20240902_193754.jpg?format=original)

